# Auto Job Application Platform

This Python application automatically searches for jobs, customizes your CV and cover letter using AI, and sends applications via email.

## Features

- Job scraping from Indeed
- AI-powered CV customization using Hugging Face Transformers
- Cover letter generation
- Email automation with self-healing retries

## Setup

1. **Clone the repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/auto-job-apply.git
   cd auto-job-apply
